File: Eskom says the loss of three additional generation units is behind the decision to implement stage 2 load-shedding. JOHANNESBURG - Eskom will implement stage 2 load-shedding on Thursday night from 10pm to 5am Friday morning. Eskom says the loss of three additional generation units is behind the decision to implement stage 2 load-shedding. The power utility confirmed the load-shedding on twitter.